# Fonts Context (MDC)

GOAL:
Typography must be completely flexible. The system must support dynamic font swapping, Google Fonts integration, and custom user-uploaded fonts. Defaults must remain clean and minimal.

REQUIREMENTS:
- Provide centralized font loading (Google Fonts + custom fonts).
- Allow per-component or global hot swapping of fonts.
- Allow custom uploaded fonts (TTF/OTF/WOFF/WOFF2).
- Keep Tailwind font configuration clean, minimal, and extensible.
- Maintain the minimalist design philosophy (calm, clear, functional).
- Avoid hardcoded typography. All font choices must be overridable.
- Ensure accessibility: readable size defaults and scalable line height.

